    <title type="html"><![CDATA[sshd设置信任登录遇到的问题]]></title>
    <link href="http://luxiaobin.github.com/blog/blog/2012/12/02/sshd-ssh-keygen-t-rsa/"/>
    <updated>2012-12-02T15:54:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://luxiaobin.github.com/blog/blog/2012/12/02/sshd-ssh-keygen-t-rsa</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>按照常规方式设置过程：</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='bash'><span class='line'><span class="nv">$mkdir</span> .ssh
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$cd</span> .ssh
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ssh</span>-keygen -t rsa
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$scp</span> id_rsa.pub root@192.168.1.33:~/.ssh
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ssh</span> -l root 192.168.1.33//远程连接到远程主机
</span><span class='line'><span class="c">#cd ./ssh</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="c">#cat id_rsa.pub &gt;&gt; authorized_keys</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$ssh</span> -l root 192.168.1.33//测试
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">$Agent</span> admitted failure to sign using the key //要求输入密码，并报错
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>检查目录权限等没问题，一般./ssh文件夹是755 authorized-keys为600或者644，搜索得到如下解决方法：在客户机ssh-add   ~/.ssh/id-rsa。更改后可以无密码登录，主要是由于客户机有多个rsa key。</p>
]]></content>
